<Chapter Label="Chapter_Salvetti_complexes">
<Heading>Salvetti complexes</Heading>

<P/>
 The Salvetti complex is a finite regular CW-complex
 having the homotopy type of the complement of a complexified real arrangement.
 It is constructed from the associated oriented matroid.
